        </ul>
      </li>

      <li class="header">USEFUL LINKS</li>
      <li>
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/danniemagalhaes/" target="_blank">
          <i class="fa fa-circle-o text-yellow"></i> <span>Dannie's LinkedIn</span>
        </a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="https://github.com/seliksy/lemonade" target="_blank">
          <i class="fa fa-circle-o text-aqua"></i> <span>Lemonade on Github</span>
